        <item>
            <title>Waymo 强调其服务不会利用内部摄影机拍摄资料向乘客投放定向广告</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;过去经常透过拆解 App 编码内容，借此挖掘各厂商接下来可能推行服务的香港工程师&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:1;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://mashdigi.com/twitter-would-release-article-function-soon/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:黄文津;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;黄文津&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;span&gt;Jane Manchun Wong&lt;/span&gt;)，稍早从 Waymo 非正式版 App 发现相关可让乘客选择不让自驾车内部摄影镜头拍摄资料用于训练人工智慧的选项，进而推测 Waymo 可能会以此功能向乘客投放贴近个人喜好的定向广告内容。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container caas-img-loader&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img caas-lazy has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;Waymo 强调其服务不会利用内部摄影机拍摄资料向乘客投放定向广告&quot; src=&quot;https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-04/d1a31dd0-186f-11f0-9bdd-1ef25fa11244&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;caption-collapse&quot;&gt;Waymo 强调其服务不会利用内部摄影机拍摄资料向乘客投放定向广告&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;不过，WaymoJulia Ilina 随后&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:2;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/news/644770/waymo-interior-camera-ai-training-ads-privacy&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:对此回应;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;对此回应&lt;/a&gt;，强调 Waymo 不会利用此类数据学习识别个人，同时也不会利用这些数据向乘客投放定向广告。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;而 Julia Ilina 也表示黄文津所找到非正式版 App 编码内容并未反应该功能实际用途，更强调相关功能仍处于开发阶段。对于黄文津所找到描述内容，Julia Ilina 表示主要是让乘客能选择避免个资被用于 Waymo 服务背后的机器学习训练，同时也说明 Waymo 的隐私政策并未作任何改变。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;twitter-tweet-wrapper&quot; data-embed-anchor=&quot;b48a594d-1ebe-54b9-b352-ad0753ac584b&quot;&gt;&lt;blockquote placeholder=&quot;&quot; data-theme=&quot;light&quot; class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-card-loader small fixed-height&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Waymo is working on Generative AI training using 「interior camera data associated with rider’s identity,」 provides opt-opts for this and data sharing under CCPA Waymo explicitly states in this unreleased Privacy page it may share your data for personalized ads &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/wDUu867Eh3&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:pic.twitter.com/wDUu867Eh3;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;pic.twitter.com/wDUu867Eh3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;— Jane Manchun Wong (@wongmjane) &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/wongmjane/status/1908629210123677901?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:April 5, 2025;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;April 5, 2025&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;目前 Waymo 的自驾车服务已经扩展到美国境内超过 10 个城市，不久前更&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:3;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://mashdigi.com/waymo-expands-its-self-driving-ride-hailing-service-to-silicon-valley-bay-area-and-more/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:宣布;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;宣布&lt;/a&gt;在旧金山湾区</description>
            <link>https://tw.news.yahoo.com/waymo-says-its-service-wont-use-internal-camera-data-to-target-passengers-with-ads-140342435.html</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/waymo-says-its-service-wont-use-internal-camera-data-to-target-passengers-with-ads-140342435.html</guid>
            <pubDate>Sun, 13 Apr 2025 14:03:42 GMT</pubDate>
            <author>Mashdigi @Mashdigi</author>
